I" <ol>
  <li>Log-in to Domain Controller</li>
  <li>Reboot into DSRM:
    <div class="language-powershell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nf">bcdedit</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/set</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">safeboot</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">dsrepair</span><span class="w"> 
</span><span class="nf">shutdown</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nt">-t</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">0</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nt">-r</span><span class="w"> 
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Run Database Check:
    <div class="language-powershell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nf">esentutl</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/g</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">c:\Windows\NTDS\ntds.dit</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="nx">10240</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/8</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/o</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>If the check returns <strong>CORRUPTED</strong>, run <code class="highlighter-rouge">ntdsutil</code> for <em>Soft Recovery</em>:
    <div class="language-powershell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nf">activate</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">instance</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">ntds</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">files</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">recover</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">quit</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">quit</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Delete <em>LOG</em> and <em>CHK</em> files:
    <div class="language-powershell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nf">del</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">c:\Windows\NTDS\</span><span class="o">*.</span><span class="nf">log</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nx">del</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">c:\Windows\NTDS\</span><span class="o">*.</span><span class="nf">chk</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Run <em>Hard Recovery</em>:
    <div class="language-powershell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nf">esentutl</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/p</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">c:\Windows\NTDS\ntds.dit</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="nx">10240</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/8</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/o</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Run <code class="highlighter-rouge">ntdsutil</code> again:
    <div class="language-powershell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nf">activate</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">instance</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">ntds</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">semantic</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">database</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">analysis</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">go</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">go</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">fix</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">quit</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">quit</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Run Database Check, again:
    <div class="language-powershell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nf">esentutl</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/g</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">c:\Windows\NTDS\ntds.dit</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/</span><span class="o">!</span><span class="nx">10240</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/8</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/o</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Disable DSRM and Reboot:
    <div class="language-powershell highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nf">bcdedit</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">/deletevalue</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">safeboot</span><span class="w">
</span><span class="nf">shutdown</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nt">-t</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nx">0</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="nt">-r</span><span class="w">
</span></code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
